Package org.vanted.indexednodes

Provides graph data structures (and operations on them) that are more efficient for some purposes.
Since:
2.8.0
Version:
1.0
Author:
David Boetius, Benjamin Halbritter, Thomas Komander, Silvan Reiner, Josua Sattler, Jakob Wietstock, Benjamin Moser
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    IndexAttribute
    Stores indices for nodes to allow fast index finding.
    IndexedComponent  
    IndexedEdgeList
    A list of edges
    IndexedGraphOperations
    Some graph operations backed by org.vanted.addons.indexednodes.IndexedNodeSet.
    IndexedNodeSet
    A node collection that supports indexed access and fast index finding as well as speedy set operations.
